  <body>
		<div class='columns'>
			<div class='document__title'>
				<h1>Video Length Calculator</h1>
				<p>Each of our "videos" here has a data attribute with its length which looks like this: <code>data-time="07:57"</code> (mins, seconds). This challenge queries them and calculates the total.</p>
			</div>
			<div class='output'>
				<p class='output__text'>
					Watch Length:
					<span class='output__data'> 00:00</span>
				</p>
			</div>
			<h2 class='videos__title'>Available Videos</h2>
			<div class='column videos'>
				<div class='bg'></div>
			</div>
			<h2 class='queue__title'>Queue</h2>
			<div class='column queue'>
				<div class='bg'></div>
			</div>
		</div>
  </body>
  <script type="text/javascript" src='/18. Tally Video Lengths/public/js/index.js'></script>
